  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can weave a veil of psychic static to mask yourself. As a Magic action, you gain the &amp;Reference[invisible] condition for 1 hour or until you dismiss this effect (no action required). This invisibility ends early immediately after you deal damage to a creature or you force a creature to make a saving throw.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest, unless you expend a Psionic Energy Die (no action required) to restore your use of it.</p><section id=\"secret-kphVDbNtMPCUXnxs\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Psychic Veil (Free)</strong> activity contains a free use. The <strong>Psychic Veil</strong> activity consumes a Psionic Die. They both include an Active Effect that applies the Invisible condition.</p></section>",
